      "content": "idk im just really overwhelmed with the travel stuff. it feels more like my heart is racing because i'm nervous rather than something else. i wouldnt want to waste time at a hospital in duba for just anxiety, i'm sure it will pass if i just sit down and try to relax. u think some deep breathing or maybe a calming tea would fix it?",
